WEBVTT

00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:12.900
A short, non-confidential guardianship inquiry.

00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:19.900
One click starts the intake workflow.

00:00:19.900 --> 00:00:28.233
Routed as guardianship — high confidence.

00:00:28.233 --> 00:00:35.233
The firm receives the real inquiry.

00:00:35.233 --> 00:00:43.733
The client reply is topical, not generic.

00:00:43.733 --> 00:00:53.733
Real availability. A 15-minute hold.

00:00:53.733 --> 00:01:07.066
Stripe test checkout reserves the consultation.

00:01:07.066 --> 00:01:11.066
A verified $50 sandbox deposit.

00:01:11.066 --> 00:01:16.066
The redirect alone does not confirm the booking.

00:01:16.066 --> 00:01:26.066
Webhook verified. Appointment confirmed.
